<h3>Calculate Your SEO ROI</h3>
<p>Use this formula to <a href="/blog/measure-content-marketing-roi/">measure content marketing ROI</a>:</p>
<p><strong>Monthly SEO value = (Monthly organic leads) x (Close rate) x (Average student lifetime value)</strong></p>
<p>Example: A tutoring center gets 40 organic leads per month. They close 25% (10 students). Each student pays $200 per month for 6 months ($1,200 lifetime value). Monthly SEO value = 10 x $1,200 = $12,000.</p>
